snippet.title: Curilemu - Trailer
snippet.description:
Curilemu

Curilemu is an adventure-horror game inspired by the myths and legends of Chilean Patagonia. Immerse yourself in a haunting world filled with Lovecraftian horrors and ancient mysteries. Fight colossal beasts and discover what is behind the plague to heal this island and restore the cosmic balance.

Obtenlo/Get It/ Obtê-lo: https://steam.curilemu.com/
Redes/Socials/Redes Sociais: https://www.instagram.com/curilemugame/  https://twitter.com/curilemugame
